  "detailed_description": "Car Looper is a tricky and challenging puzzle experience.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1543650/extras/ff17526cd6cce461a7d15a268126abf3.poster.avif?t=1627380668\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1543650/extras/ff17526cd6cce461a7d15a268126abf3.webm?t=1627380668\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1543650/extras/ff17526cd6cce461a7d15a268126abf3.mp4?t=1627380668\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You are the manager of a racetrack and have to build looping tracks before the time runs out.<br>Use different tiles to avoid obstacles and create the longest track possible!<br><br>Try your puzzle solving skills in one of two different game modes:<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1543650/extras/b0ff16d85c985c8bc629452e05508253.avif?t=1627380668\" width=798 height=200 /></span><br>In exploration mode you have no timelimit to create your track. <br>You can try to perfect your track and get the best score possible without the ticking clock!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1543650/extras/34362c040dc43f0afa756d9baa9be893.avif?t=1627380668\" width=800 height=200 /></span><br>In time mode it is all about speed!<br>Try to build your track while the clock is ticking down!",
  "about_the_game": "Car Looper is a tricky and challenging puzzle experience.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1543650/extras/ff17526cd6cce461a7d15a268126abf3.poster.avif?t=1627380668\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1543650/extras/ff17526cd6cce461a7d15a268126abf3.webm?t=1627380668\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1543650/extras/ff17526cd6cce461a7d15a268126abf3.mp4?t=1627380668\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You are the manager of a racetrack and have to build looping tracks before the time runs out.<br>Use different tiles to avoid obstacles and create the longest track possible!<br><br>Try your puzzle solving skills in one of two different game modes:<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1543650/extras/b0ff16d85c985c8bc629452e05508253.avif?t=1627380668\" width=798 height=200 /></span><br>In exploration mode you have no timelimit to create your track. <br>You can try to perfect your track and get the best score possible without the ticking clock!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1543650/extras/34362c040dc43f0afa756d9baa9be893.avif?t=1627380668\" width=800 height=200 /></span><br>In time mode it is all about speed!<br>Try to build your track while the clock is ticking down!",
